General.Name: Ark Mines Limited
General.Description: Ark Mines Limited focuses in the mineral exploration and mining business in Australia. The company holds 100% interests in the Gunnawarra Project covering an area of 34.1 ha; Pluton Gold Project covering an area of 18.6 ha; and Mount Jesse Iron with Copper project that covers an area of 12.4 ha located in Australia. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
